caption:
Liquid VO2 is the orange colour corrector you’ve come to know and love! But what sets it apart… 🤔 

It’s the signature peach colour! 

The unique shade of orange effectively cancels out dark circles and hyperpigmentation while brightening the area for the ultimate finish. 

The lightweight texture and formula makes it easy for you to use alone or underneath other makeup! 

How do you use Liquid VO2? Let us know!
